value.name: Welcome to London - visitlondon.com
value.snippet: Welcome to London! Discover the best of London with Visit London, the official guide to England’s exciting capital. Find things to do in London, from iconic sightseeing spots and fun-filled days out to top restaurants, theatre and unmissable London events. If you’re not able to visit just yet, plan ahead to make the most of your next visit.

value.name: London - Wikipedia
value.snippet: London is the capital and largest city of England and the United Kingdom, with a population of just under 9 million. It stands on the River Thames in south-east England at the head of a 50-mile (80 km) estuary down to the North Sea, and has been a major settlement for two millennia.

value.name: London | History, Maps, Population, Area, & Facts | Britannica
value.snippet: London is one of the world’s most cosmopolitan cities. It is the largest metropolis in the United Kingdom, and it is also the country’s economic, transportation, and cultural centre. In addition to its history, art, and politics, London is a popular tourist destination for its wide variety of museums, shops, restaurants, and sports teams.

value.name: Seværdigheder i London - 16 af Londons bedste oplevelser 🇬🇧
value.snippet: Nogle af de mest populære seværdigheder i London er bl.a. London Eye, Buckingham Palace, Tower of London og Bog Ben. Disse seværdigheder beskriver jeg i indlægget her, men London har langt mere at byde på end de mest populære seværdigheder, så overvej også at opsøge oplevelser såsom Brick Lane, Camden Market og Greenwich Park.

value.name: Top 10 London attractions - London Attraction - visitlondon.com
value.snippet: From the modern London Eye to the historic Tower of London, the top 10 tourist attractions in London are a must-see on any London sightseeing trip. Even better, many London landmarks are free to visit. Use the Londo n attractions map to find them all. There are also plenty of kid-friendly places to visit in London.

value.name: London, England 2023: Best Places to Visit - Tripadvisor
value.snippet: A regal city surrounded by a rush of modern life. London is layered with history, where medieval and Victorian complement a rich and vibrant modern world. The Tower of London and Westminster neighbor local pubs and markets, and time-worn rituals like the changing of the guards take place as commuters rush to catch the Tube.

value.name: Rejser til London med fly og hotel | Spies
value.snippet: London har mange historiske monumenter og interessante seværdigheder med fantastisk design og arkitektur. Nogle af de mest populære seværdigheder er Tower Bridge, Tower of London, St. Paul's Cathedral, Westminster Abbey, Buckingham Palace, Kensington Palace og Trafalgar Square.
